  %% Diagram 10: Order Saga - Distributed Transaction (5 Steps + Compensating Actions)

  Start([PlaceOrderCommand Received]) --> I0{Idempotency Key Seen?}
  I0 -- Yes --> Prev[Return Prior Saga Outcome]
  I0 -- No --> S1[Step 1: Reserve Inventory]

  S1 --> D1{Inventory Reserved?}
  D1 -- No --> F1[Fail: Out of Stock\nReturn 409]
  D1 -- Yes --> S2[Step 2: Process Payment]

  S2 --> D2{Payment Captured and Verified?}
  D2 -- No --> C21[Compensate: Release Inventory]
  C21 --> F2[OrderFailedCompensated]
  D2 -- Yes --> S3[Step 3: Hold Escrow]

  S3 --> D3{Escrow Held?}
  D3 -- No --> C31[Compensate: Refund Payment]
  C31 --> C32[Compensate: Release Inventory]
  C32 --> F3[OrderFailedCompensated]
  D3 -- Yes --> S4[Step 4: Confirm Order]

  S4 --> D4{Order Confirmed?}
  D4 -- No --> C41[Compensate: Refund Payment]
  C41 --> C42[Compensate: Release Inventory]
  C42 --> F4[OrderFailedCompensated]
  D4 -- Yes --> S5[Step 5: Assign Logistics]

  S5 --> D5{Logistics Assigned?}
  D5 -- No --> C51[Compensate: Refund Payment]
  C51 --> C52[Compensate: Release Inventory]
  C52 --> F5[OrderFailedCompensated + Manual Retry Queue]
  D5 -- Yes --> OK[OrderConfirmedSagaComplete]

  OK --> N1[Notify Buyer + Vendor\nEmit success events]
  F2 --> N2[Notify Buyer + Vendor\nEmit failure events]
  F3 --> N3[Notify Buyer + Vendor + Finance]
  F4 --> N4[Notify Buyer + Vendor + Finance]
  F5 --> N5[Notify Buyer + Vendor + Support + Finance/Admin]

  F1 --> A0[Append audit_logs + correlation ID]
  N1 --> A0
  N2 --> A0
  N3 --> A0
  N4 --> A0
  N5 --> A0
